videos.description: Spencer Sanders finds Jordan McCray in the back corner of the end zone to score a Oklahoma State touchdown to cut Baylor's lead to 7-6.

videos.description: Baylor retakes the lead in the fourth quarter as Charlie Brewer rushes in through the Oklahoma State defense to score a two-yard touchdown.
